{"tid":2357120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布 美國準備發生內戰","createTime":"2021-01-07T08:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T20:52:48.000Z","uid":365231,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"21e75a21cf68e2b6198264c5deaad4b903ea75c4","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8WFv9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8WFv9m.jpg&h=c353c50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自從11月3號既美國大選之後 我就有預感美國有可能發動內戰 所以我就睇咗啲係架空世界(遊戲)發生既美國內戰。見到Trump係到吹大雞 等陣可以再講下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZL5GfDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZL5GfDh.png&h=d55855da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖係上年大選每州得票既圖 內戰爆發最保守既地圖就係爆成咁 尤其係拜登啲得票好fake 保證唔到有啲藍色既州爆發內戰 就一定係拜登<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁架空世界發生既美國內戰 就不得不提<span class=\"large\"><strong><em><ins><span class=\"red\">Heart of Iron V</span></ins></em></strong></span> 係一個二次大戰下既遊戲背景 你可以扮演任何既國家。 咁又關美國內戰咩事呢?<br />\n<br />\n咁我哋就講下係遊戲裡面既美國國策<br />\n<img src=\"https://hoi4.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/2/2f/NF_tree_USA.jpg/1280px-NF_tree_USA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhoi4.paradoxwikis.com%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2F2%2F2f%2FNF_tree_USA.jpg%2F1280px-NF_tree_USA.jpg&h=4b832f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次我哋主要講既係 左(共產主義)/右(法西斯主義)既國策 因為佢哋會令到美國爆發內戰。<br />\n<br />\n內戰前夕<br />\n政府軍械庫被突襲 聯邦政府既稅收被扣留 國民警衛隊既編隊被動員和訓練 直到宣布脫離聯邦--＞打響內戰<br />\n爆發內戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwm2KLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frwm2KLt.jpg&h=2925b5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆發內戰後 佢有個決議類似政府招募民兵 咁就有一堆兵黎幫助你打贏內戰啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁宜家我哋講下真正既美國內戰幾時會黎料。<br />\n<br />\n第一，係Game 裡面會有政府軍械庫被突襲，暫時未見到(如果真係有 都會係安提法既民兵)<br />\n<br />\n第二，國民警衛隊既編隊被動員和訓練，係安提法搞暴動嗰陣已經開始有了。宜家只係等啲地方政府幾時脫離聯邦政府。<br />\n<br />\n第三，Trump開始為民眾同軍人吹大雞了。就佢去西點軍校同埋今日既華盛頓集會。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POKDiRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOKDiRH.jpg&h=4406dd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1569037_1_20210107033126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1569037_1_20210107033126.jpg&h=8e0d9f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n種種跡象見到內戰既影子，除非任何一方投降，如果唔係內戰既機會係好大。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">1月20日</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"174df5084d5114283fd23ca284d9411763e2f795","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7f491af21453516e64a25dad715a0b85a2da5b57","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cfc36e2269864ef8f9cd1f4afac0a243cf8aa6e9","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ea1a56704380567027d00ee199b9f66f4e848b45","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"879a171ec0436a74c9aa80f529c3ca2ed7f47216","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35176f871dc3685547b0827c0c8f8c061f425653","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f30e6e4cef42c27ade9537e27bea646001fda079","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:38:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15e07833fa84b93ebbd7f0b1ec981f35a9c8e58c","tid":2357120,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4bea723a2aa32d0daf43cbd1006b4606aa3a9bfa","tid":2357120,"uid":24264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T19:16:00.000Z","msg